
# Security and Backup

## 1. Security Measures
- User authentication via secure login
- Role-based access control (Member, Active Member, Leader, Admin)
- Encryption of sensitive data in database
- BV and income-related calculations protected in system backend

## 2. Data Backup
- Regular database backups (daily/weekly as per system requirement)
- Backup stored securely on cloud (AWS or equivalent)
- Restore procedures documented and tested

## 3. Disaster Recovery
- Contingency plan for system failure
- Critical data recovery from backups
- Step-by-step recovery documentation

## 4. Notes
- BV calculations, product records, and activation logs included in backup
- Security policies updated as system evolves
- No user income or personal financial data is exposed publicly
